### Base URL — override per environment
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080


### [AGRO] Missing areaBeneficiadaHa → 422 Unprocessable Entity
###   Rejected by use case before reaching the product service
POST {{baseUrl}}/operacoes-credito
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idAssociado": 3,
  "valorOperacao": 5000,
  "segmento": "AGRO",
  "codigoProdutoCredito": "303C",
  "codigoConta": "1111111111"
}

###

### [AGRO] areaBeneficiadaHa = 0 → 422 Unprocessable Entity
###   Zero is explicitly rejected by AGRO validation rule
POST {{baseUrl}}/operacoes-credito
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idAssociado": 3,
  "valorOperacao": 5000,
  "segmento": "AGRO",
  "codigoProdutoCredito": "303C",
  "codigoConta": "1111111111",
  "areaBeneficiadaHa": 0
}
